msg: Undeprected the XByteBuffer.createDataPackage, I want to avoid spreading code that belongs together across multiple classes.
That way, when changes are needed for the protocol, it can be implemented in this place, and not affect everything else.
In 5.5 the Sender.isSuspect has become cluttered, error messages are reported and ignoring this flag.
I have started to clean up the code to use the suspect flag again, to avoid over flowing the logs.
